  "title": "John Savill's Top of Mind",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Sarah talk with guest John Savill&nbsp;(<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://linkedin.com/in/john-savill'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a> <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/NTFAQGuy'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>)\n                  about a few security items that are top of mind for him, and what he is hearing from customers. We also cover news from Microsoft Build, Michael's new book, as well as the latest post-quantum crypto news.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/2910710?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2910710/\">JohnSavillsTop</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5>\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2910710/#transcript'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FFMm454fxNA\">Microsoft Build 2026 | Satya Nadella Opening Keynote</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8QBDaRbur70&list=PPSV\">MDASH: Microsoft Build 2026 (Sarah's demo)</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azuresqlblog/transparent-data-encryption-in-azure-sql-database-now-supports-aes-keys-public-p/4523240\">Transparent data encryption in Azure SQL Database now supports AES keys (Public Preview)</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/microsoft-security-blog/new-windows-features-to-secure-today%E2%80%99s-data-in-a-post-quantum-world/4523370\">New Windows Features to Secure Today’s Data in a Post-Quantum World</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/0135567386/\">Threat-Driven Software Development (Michael's new book)</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@NTFAQGuy\">John Savill&#39;s Technical Training</a></li>\n                  </ul>"
